snippet.title: Car Destroyer
snippet.description: Car Destroyer Car game. Set the ramp and the speed of the car to make it fly and demolish all cars each level.

snippet.title: Rich Cars 3: Hustle
snippet.description: Rich Cars 3: Hustle Racing game. Try to get all your cars back racing the tracks to earn cash. Buy all cars back!

snippet.title: Cargo Bridge 2
snippet.description: Cargo Bridge 2 Build bridges using wood, rope and other stuff to transport the cargo from one end to the other.

snippet.title: Speed Cards
snippet.description: Speed Cards Get rid of your cards before the computer does by placing your cards on one of the two middle piles.

snippet.title: Stonehenge Solitaire
snippet.description: Stonehenge Solitaire Card game. Various types of the cards game solitaire can be played. Prove your cardplayer skills!

snippet.title: Cargo Bridge
snippet.description: Cargo Bridge Physics puzzle game. Build a bridge with limited money which is strong enough to hold the cargo.

snippet.title: Cardboard Box Assembler
snippet.description: Cardboard Box Assembler Platform puzzle. Help Melvin to overcome a mental breakdown reaching the exit.

snippet.title: Car Ferry
snippet.description: Car Ferry Physics puzzle. Get the car on the ferry using items to build bridges with to get to the next level.

snippet.title: Cards Wars
snippet.description: Cards Wars Strategy game. Try to conquer the world using the highest sets of cards in this turn based game.

snippet.title: World of Mutants 2: Reincarnation
snippet.description: World of Mutants 2: Reincarnation Sidescrolling action shooter. Remove the nasty aliens from all six planets.
